Html:
I use ModenUI Charts within all of my mui projects just fine. I just added this to my resource dictionary in App.xaml<br />
<pre><code>&lt;Style x:Key=&quot;MinimalChartStyle&quot; TargetType=&quot;chart:ChartBase&quot;&gt;
                &lt;Setter Property=&quot;MinWidth&quot; Value=&quot;450&quot; /&gt;
                &lt;Setter Property=&quot;MinHeight&quot; Value=&quot;400&quot; /&gt;
                &lt;Setter Property=&quot;TextOptions.TextFormattingMode&quot; Value=&quot;Ideal&quot; /&gt;
&lt;/Style&gt;</code></pre>
